actual = type1.is_assignable(type2)
assert actual == result
pytest.mark.parametrize('type1, type2, result', [(Integer, Integer, True),
    (Integer, Real, False), (Real, Integer, True), (Bool, Bool, True), (
    Bool, Integer, False), (List(Integer), List(Integer), True), (List(Real
    ), List(Integer), False), (Set(Integer), List(Integer), False)])
